data.description: Welcome home to this beautiful brick ranch! Three bed and one full bath with lots of open space. Hardwood floors and updates throughout. Spacious living areas and a huge basement that can be converted to anything you dream. Outside is a spacious backyard that is perfect for relaxing, entertaining, pets and kids. Two car detached garage with power garage door and concrete driveway. Enjoy this quite neighborhood while being minutes from all the attractions of downtown Xenia. Do no miss this great home in a great location! Low interest rate assumable financing option!
